highlights.text: KPop Demon Hunters Cast has the most spots on Viral Songs Australia. “Golden” is the highest at #2.
“The Glen - Levi Heron Edit” by Levi Heron has been on Viral Songs Australia the longest, at 96 days straight.
“yellowstone (holding you)” by Matt Hansen is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Australia, up 9 spots at #67.
“Fine (feat. Paul Kelly)” by Meg Washington and Paul Kelly is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Australia at #79.
